data-v-182d5fe2="" class="">Copy</span></div></div></header> <div data-v-efb858b9="" data-v-782faaad="" class="syntax-highlighter dark segment-code-content"><pre data-v-efb858b9="" class="language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token doctype"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;!</span><span class="token doctype-tag">DOCTYPE</span> <span class="token name">html</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
